data.name: textBox1.Text
data.value:
Battleships is a guessing game for two players. Here you are a fleet captain and you have 5 warships - 3 Destroyers, 1 Battleship and 1 Aircraft Carrier. Your mission is to destroy and sink all of the enemy ships.
First you need to put all of your warships in position. Your sea is on the left side of the screen and the enemy sea is on the right. You can pick which warship you want to place and whether you want to place it horizontally or vertically. After the battle has started you have the first move, you can fire first. If you hit an enemy ship then it's your turn again so try to destroy it. If you miss then it's the opponent's turn.
The player that destroyes every Battleship of the opponent is the winner.
Good luck, captain!
